(53, 2, '2014-03-06 15:46:52', '2014-03-06 14:46:52', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur ultricies tortor sed lorem pharetra, vitae malesuada lectus bibendum. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Curabitur sagittis dictum justo, eu gravida mi vehicula vel. Donec lacinia felis in orci pharetra interdum at non elit. Phasellus eu nulla est. In purus orci, volutpat quis odio eu, bibendum mollis libero. Donec laoreet, velit quis vulputate commodo, turpis quam dapibus tellus, at blandit odio ligula id dolor. Maecenas ornare lectus vitae lectus aliquam fringilla. Nulla facilisi. Duis pulvinar magna eget accumsan blandit. Pellentesque lorem est, tempus auctor risus vel, dignissim malesuada nulla. Nulla facilisi.', 'Designing for emotion', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur ultricies tortor sed lorem pharetra.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'designing-for-emotion', '', '', '2017-02-16 10:12:22', '2017-02-16 09:12:22', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-books&#038;p=53', 0, 'bks-books', '', 0),
(62, 2, '2014-03-06 15:55:57', '2014-03-06 14:55:57', 'Orders ship within 24 hours of being placed. Shipping time in the US is usually less than a week; in the UK and Canada, shipping time is generally 7-10 business days. Elsewhere in Europe, shipping time can be 3-4 weeks. To all other locations, please allow 4-6 weeks for your book to arrive.', 'Where’s my book?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wheres-my-book', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:55:57', '2014-03-06 14:55:57', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=62', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(63, 2, '2014-03-06 15:56:42', '2014-03-06 14:56:42', 'We ship books worldwide.', 'Where do you ship to?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'where-do-you-ship-to', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:56:42', '2014-03-06 14:56:42', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=63', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(64, 2, '2014-03-06 15:57:00', '2014-03-06 14:57:00', 'Shipping is calculated during checkout after you enter your shipping address; you will be able to review the shipping charges before placing your order. In the US, you may choose between the USPS or UPS for shipping for small orders; for orders over 10 books in the US, UPS shipping is required. Outside the US, orders ship via the USPS.\n\nNote that we charge for shipping in line with our costs, and work to keep those costs as low as we can. International shipping prices are higher than we would like them to be, and we are looking into other options to reduce these costs — including a European distributor. But for now, the USPS remains the most affordable way to get physical books to you around the world.', 'What do you charge for shipping?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-do-you-charge-for-shipping', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:57:00', '2014-03-06 14:57:00', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=64', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(65, 2, '2014-03-06 15:57:20', '2014-03-06 14:57:20', 'For orders shipped via the USPS, no tracking information is provided; for orders shipped via UPS, tracking information will be sent to you when the order is shipped.', 'What’s my tracking number?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'whats-my-tracking-number', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:57:20', '2014-03-06 14:57:20', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=65', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(66, 2, '2014-03-06 15:57:37', '2014-03-06 14:57:37', 'We attach the appropriate customs forms to every international shipment and clearly label the contents as “books;” many countries do not levy customs taxes on the importation of books, so in most cases, no customs fees will be applied. That said, any import taxes charged by the destination country are your responsibility. Customs policies vary widely from country to country so if you have any concerns before you order, we recommend that you contact your local customs office.', 'How do you handle international customs, taxes, or duties?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-you-handle-international-customs-taxes-or-duties', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:57:37', '2014-03-06 14:57:37', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=66', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(67, 2, '2014-03-06 15:58:00', '2014-03-06 14:58:00', 'Ok; let us know your order number and the correct address, and we’ll do our best to get it fixed up for you. Orders ship out very quickly, so there’s no guarantee we’ll be able to make corrections to an order before it ships.', 'Oops! I gave you the wrong shipping address.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oops-i-gave-you-the-wrong-shipping-address', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:58:00', '2014-03-06 14:58:00', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=67', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(68, 2, '2014-03-06 15:58:23', '2014-03-06 14:58:23', 'Unfortunately, we can only accept addresses using the Latin alphabet due to the rules of our shipping partners. All non-Latin character addresses will result in the order being non-deliverable.', 'I have a shipping address with non-Latin characters. Can you ship to it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'i-have-a-shipping-address-with-non-latin-characters-can-you-ship-to-it', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:58:23', '2014-03-06 14:58:23', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=68', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(69, 2, '2014-03-06 15:58:37', '2014-03-06 14:58:37', 'When you checkout, you can apply your gift card code after you enter your shipping and billing information (but before you confirm your order). There’s a specific field just for gift cards!', 'I have a gift card. How do I redeem it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'i-have-a-gift-card-how-do-i-redeem-it', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:58:37', '2014-03-06 14:58:37', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=69', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(70, 2, '2014-03-06 15:59:10', '2014-03-06 14:59:10', 'When you purchase a gift card, you’ll get an email with instructions on how to view, share, and print it. To share a gift card, simply forward that email to the recipient, or share the gift card link (also included in the email) directly.', 'I bought a gift card for someone else. How do I share it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'i-bought-a-gift-card-for-someone-else-how-do-i-share-it', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:59:10', '2014-03-06 14:59:10', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=70', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(71, 2, '2014-03-06 15:59:29', '2014-03-06 14:59:29', 'Shortly after your order for the ebook goes through, you’ll receive an email with a link to download your book. Check your spam folder if you don’t see it right away.', 'I ordered the ebook. When will I get it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'i-ordered-the-ebook-when-will-i-get-it', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:59:29', '2014-03-06 14:59:29', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=71', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(72, 2, '2014-03-06 15:59:52', '2014-03-06 14:59:52', 'Yes, of course. Just visit this page and enter your order number and the email address used to place the order. We’ll give you a new link to download the files.', 'My cat ate my ebook files. Can I download the ebook again?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-cat-ate-my-ebook-files-can-i-download-the-ebook-again', '', '', '2014-03-06 15:59:52', '2014-03-06 14:59:52', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=72', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(73, 2, '2014-03-06 16:00:12', '2014-03-06 15:00:12', 'Drop us a line with your order number (or the email address used to place the order), and we’ll reset your download link.', 'My download link expired; how can I download my ebook?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-download-link-expired-how-can-i-download-my-ebook', '', '', '2014-03-06 16:00:12', '2014-03-06 15:00:12', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?post_type=bks-faqs&amp;p=73', 0, 'bks-faqs', '', 0),
(74, 2, '2014-03-07 10:27:12', '2014-03-07 09:27:12', '<b>Tech Talk</b>\r\n\r\nThe <a href="http://www.themosis.com/">Themosis PHP Framework</a> looks like other modern PHP frameworks such as Laravel and it\'s designed specifically for WordPress. <i>And</i> it\'s made in Belgium.\r\n\r\nI\'m very excited that the Julien Lambé, the creator of Themosis, has agreed to come and present the framework to the group.\r\n\r\n<i>This will be a technical talk aimed at PHP developers</i> or people that are learning PHP.\r\n\r\nInteger rhoncus ligula velit, et rhoncus urna molestie ac. Etiam convallis ac purus eu placerat. Integer quis vestibulum lacus. Sed eu ligula ac arcu consectetur lacinia sed porttitor massa. Pellentesque interdum lacus in justo semper, in lacinia diam convallis. Quisque molestie leo et nisl tempor aliquet. Nam a ante vel arcu varius scelerisque non eu ante. Sed in bibendum turpis. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Pellentesque feugiat sodales nibh ut auctor. Aliquam cursus erat in imperdiet suscipit. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Vestibulum dapibus magna ac justo gravida ultrices. Sed sed consequat quam. Proin faucibus nisl lectus, et eleifend tortor hendrerit vitae.', 'Live from the WordPress meetup!', 'Integer rhoncus ligula velit, et rhoncus urna molestie ac. Etiam convallis ac purus eu placerat.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'live-from-the-wordpress-meetup', '', '', '2017-02-16 09:44:03', '2017-02-16 08:44:03', '', 0, 'http://bookstore.local/?p=74', 0, 'post', '', 0),
