(119, 2, '2017-02-16 09:44:03', '2017-02-16 08:44:03', '<b>Tech Talk</b>\r\n\r\nThe <a href="http://www.themosis.com/">Themosis PHP Framework</a> looks like other modern PHP frameworks such as Laravel and it\'s designed specifically for WordPress. <i>And</i> it\'s made in Belgium.\r\n\r\nI\'m very excited that the Julien Lambé, the creator of Themosis, has agreed to come and present the framework to the group.\r\n\r\n<i>This will be a technical talk aimed at PHP developers</i> or people that are learning PHP.\r\n\r\nInteger rhoncus ligula velit, et rhoncus urna molestie ac. Etiam convallis ac purus eu placerat. Integer quis vestibulum lacus. Sed eu ligula ac arcu consectetur lacinia sed porttitor massa. Pellentesque interdum lacus in justo semper, in lacinia diam convallis. Quisque molestie leo et nisl tempor aliquet. Nam a ante vel arcu varius scelerisque non eu ante. Sed in bibendum turpis. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Pellentesque feugiat sodales nibh ut auctor. Aliquam cursus erat in imperdiet suscipit. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Vestibulum dapibus magna ac justo gravida ultrices. Sed sed consequat quam. Proin faucibus nisl lectus, et eleifend tortor hendrerit vitae.', 'Live from the WordPress meetup!', 'Integer rhoncus ligula velit, et rhoncus urna molestie ac. Etiam convallis ac purus eu placerat.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-16 09:44:03', '2017-02-16 08:44:03', '', 74, 'http://bookstore.dev/2017/02/16/74-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
